text: Qal'eh Dokhtar or Ghale Dokhtar or Dokhtar Castle or Dezh Dokhtar (, "The Maiden Castle"), is a castle made by Ardashir I, in present-day Fars, Iran. == References == == Other websites == * Category:209 Category:Fars Province Category:World Heritage Sites in Iran Category:3rd-century works
title: Ghal'eh Dokhtar
